channel.title: Wagneric: Lung Cone Overture [Orchestral Soundtrack]
channel.description: [Lung Cone Overture](https://soundcloud.com/wagneric/20180603-lco) was inspired by [this story](https://www.sciencealert.com/a-suspected-case-of-lung-cancer-turned-out-to-be-a-toy-traffic-cone) about a toy traffic cone that spent 40 years in a guy's lung, which has some odd parallels to my life.
